item.title: CVE-2022-3350|2024-08-03T01:07:06.697Z -- unknown -- contact%20bank%20%E2%80%93%20contact%20form%20builder%20for%20wordpress
item.description: The Contact Bank WordPress plugin through 3.0.30 does not sanitise and escape some of its Form settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)
